1.安装jailkit运行环境

解压、编译、安装
tar -zxvf jailkit-2.19.tar.gz
cd jailkit-2.19
./configure
make
make install

2.修改jailkit初始化配置

[]jk_lsh]是jailkit运行必不可少的配置，我们为实现权限最小化，不使用默认的[basicshell]配置，在[jk_lsh]的paths中新增/bin/bash
[jk_lsh]
comment = Jailkit limited shell
paths = /usr/sbin/jk_lsh, /etc/jailkit/jk_lsh.ini,/bin/bash
users = root
groups = root
includesections = uidbasics, logbasics

本项目功能实现依赖python和ssh
新增python配置
[python]
comment = the python interpreter and libraries
paths = /usr/bin/python, /usr/bin/python2.7, /usr/lib/python2.7, /usr/lib64/python2.7, /usr/include/python2.7

初始化脚本
jk_init -v -j /opt/jail jk_lsh ssh python


3.用户配置

新建用户
useradd fortress

修改密码
passwd fortress

切换用户，生成密钥对
su fortress
ssh-keygen -t rsa

将用户迁移至jail环境
jk_jailuser -m -v -j /opt/jail/ -s /bin/bash fortress





